rbnIetfVrrpCap.name: rbnIetfVrrpCap

revisions.description: Update DESCRIPTION clause of MODULE-IDENTITY and PRODUCT-RELEASE clause of AGENT-CAPABILITIES.
Add vrrpNotificationCntl variation to indicate that VRRP notification control is disabled by default.

rbnIetfVrrpCap.description: The Agent Capabilities of the VRRP-MIB (RFC 2787). If this MIB implementation is platform-dependent, the PRODUCT-RELEASE clause contains Ericsson SEOS version and at least one of the following Ericsson product families: [SE] SmartEdge Multi-service Edge Router (MSER) family [SM] SM family of Metro Ethernet Service Transport platforms [SSR] Smart Service Router (SSR) family
